{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you can see that that day I was functioning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But part of that journey, I was out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the waves, she told me, was so big.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- by the way, we left Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was erev Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She says, we were Shabbos on the boat-- on the ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she thought-- I didn't remember any of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She remembered, my friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she-- and she said she never thought we're going to-- we're going to survive this trip.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we arrived in London, you know, erev Pesach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We arrived erev Pesach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "By the way, I'm going back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When I left Zabrze, that home, that was the first time that I celebrated Purim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I forgot to mention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was the first time that I celebrated Purim in a long, many years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I have a picture of it sitting at the table, the picture on Purim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there were fruits on the table, and fruits wasn't so easily available in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But there were oranges, I think, and you can see on the picture, and there were fruits.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and we were celebrating in the very best way, I think, the-- on the best that we could under those circumstances.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were like a happy little family, because all the children, we had one thing in common.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We all survived, and some of us less the parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was a very happy Purim because-- and that was the Purim-- the first Purim that I-- that I remember since I was a child.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't even remember before, because Purim wasn't that big.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But that was a Purim I remember I celebrated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I remember it vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And Pesach, from-- we were in London.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
